little dot symbol here.

00:00:39.190 --> 00:00:41.720
This is not a decimal, it
sits higher than a decimal,

00:00:41.720 --> 00:00:46.290
and it means multiplication,
five times t, either of these,

00:00:46.290 --> 00:00:50.690
five dot t or five t means
five times t, it makes sense.

00:00:50.690 --> 00:00:52.650
You take your speed times your time,

00:00:52.650 --> 00:00:55.750
